---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import LandingHeaderEn from "../../components/LandingHeaderEn.astro";
import FooterEn from "../../components/FooterEn.astro";
import "../../../styles/servicios-operativos.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Operational communications for large teams | VivaSpeak"
  description="Automate time tracking, incidents and unreported absences with calls, WhatsApp and email, with traceability and compliance."
  canonical="https://vivaspeak.com/en/operational-services"
  alternateEs="https://vivaspeak.com/servicios-operativos"
  alternateEn="https://vivaspeak.com/en/operational-services"
  keywords="internal communications, time tracking, absenteeism, incidents, WhatsApp Business, automated calls, HR, operations, traceability"
  ogImage="/assets/og-image.png"
  lang="en"
>
  <LandingHeaderEn
    ctaLabel="Schedule a call"
    ctaHref="https://calendly.com/vivaspeak/30min"
  />
  <main class="landing-sector">
    <section class="sector-hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid-sector">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">For multiservice companies and distributed teams</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title">
            Operational contact with 10,000+ employees, without friction or
            chaos
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            VivaSpeak coordinates calls, WhatsApp and email to control
            clock-ins, detect incidents and unreported absences, leaving
            traceability and reports ready for HR and operations.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a class="btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/vivaspeak/30min">
              Schedule a quick call
            </a>
            <a
              class="btn-secondary"
              href="mailto:alberto@vivaspeak.com?subject=VivaSpeak%20-%20Operational%20communications"
              >Contact by email</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="trust-strip">
            <div class="trust-item">
              <div class="trust-icon">10k+</div>
              <span>Built for large, distributed teams.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <div class="trust-icon">24/7</div>
              <span>Always-on availability, even outside working hours.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <div class="trust-icon">GDPR</div>
              <span>Flows with consent and full traceability.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="hero-card">
          <h3>Priority use cases</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Daily clock-in checks and confirmations.</li>
            <li>Real-time incident reporting.</li>
            <li>Detection of unreported absences.</li>
            <li>Escalation to supervisors when alerts appear.</li>
            <li>Consolidated reporting by site, area or shift.</li>
          </ul>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="sector-section-title sector-section-title--narrow">
          Structured internal communication, not just scattered messages
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lead section-lead--center">
          The difference is not just contacting people, but doing it in an
          orderly, measurable and repeatable way. VivaSpeak orchestrates
          multi-channel campaigns, collects responses and consolidates
          information in a single dashboard.
        </p>
        <div class="sector-grid">
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Smart segmentation</h4>
            <p>Campaigns by site, shift, role or service unit.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Coordinated multi-channel</h4>
            <p>WhatsApp first, then call and email if no response.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Structured responses</h4>
            <p>Clear fields for clock-ins, incidents and absences.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Automatic escalation</h4>
            <p>Alerts to supervisors when a critical incident appears.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-band">
          <strong>Outcome: daily operational control without overload.</strong>
          <p>
            You define the flow and VivaSpeak executes, records and leaves
            reports ready for internal audit.
          </p>
          <a class="btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/vivaspeak/30min">
            See fit on a call
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="sector-section-title">
          How would the pilot work for your team?
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lead section-lead--center">
          In 3 steps we can have the operational flow running and validate it
          with a representative group of employees.
        </p>
        
        <div class="workflow">
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span>1</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Process map and critical data</h4>
              <p>We define what is asked, when and to whom.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span>2</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Automation and controlled tests</h4>
              <p>We simulate clock-in, incident and absence flows.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="workflow-step">
            <span>3</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Dashboards and escalation</h4>
              <p>Consolidated results with response metrics.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-grid">
          <div class="proof-card">
            <strong>Clear KPIs</strong>
            <span>Response rates, contact times and incidents reported.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card">
            <strong>Audit trail</strong>
            <span>Full history by employee, site or service.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-card">
            <strong>Escalation</strong>
            <span>Automatic alerts to managers when risk appears.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="sector-section-title">
          Coordinated channels for maximum coverage
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lead section-lead--center">
          We use the most effective channel based on the employee profile and
          the type of communication, always with traceability.
        </p>
        <div class="sector-grid">
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>AI calls</h4>
            <p>Natural voice, confirmations and instant data capture.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Official WhatsApp</h4>
            <p>Approved templates, fast replies and follow-up.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Operational email</h4>
            <p>Summaries and evidence for HR and managers.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Control panel</h4>
            <p>Everything is logged and easy to review.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="sector-section-title">Compliance and data protection</h2>
        <p class="section-lead section-lead--center">
          Designed for companies with transparency, compliance and ESG goals.
          Flows are built with consent and minimal exposure of personal data.
        </p>
        <div class="sector-grid">
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Consent and opt-out</h4>
            <p>Messages aligned with internal policy and GDPR.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Full traceability</h4>
            <p>Record of every interaction and response.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Protected sensitive data</h4>
            <p>Role-based access and centralized reporting.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="sector-card">
            <h4>Audit-ready</h4>
            <p>Information prepared for internal reviews.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="sector-section-title">Quick questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Can we start with an initial pilot?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes, we start with a representative group and scale based on
              results and operations.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What data do you need at the beginning?</summary>
            <p>
              A segmented list, schedules and the control questions you want to
              capture (clock-ins, incidents, absences).
            </p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Does it integrate with existing internal processes?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes, we can deliver reports in the format HR and operations need
              and adapt the flow to your current process.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container final-cta">
        <h2>If it fits, letâ€™s talk this week</h2>
        <p class="final-cta-text">
          In a short call we can define the flow for clock-ins and incidents,
          and set up a fast pilot.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/vivaspeak/30min">
            Book a call
          </a>
          <a
            class="btn-secondary"
            href="mailto:alberto@vivaspeak.com?subject=VivaSpeak%20-%20Operational%20Pilot"
            >Send an email</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <FooterEn langEnHref="/en/operational-services" langEsHref="/servicios-operativos" />
</Layout>
